His Majesty's brother.)

241
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:26,100
(He's never allied
with any court faction.)

242
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:28,380
(Perhaps I can use him)

243
00:10:28,580 --> 00:10:30,260
